Rename Person to Task as per our Project aims.

Task does not require a Phone, Email or Address.

Remove Phone, Email and Address classes.
Remove Phone, Email and Address JUnit testcases.
Task will take Description as one of its paramters along with Name and Set<Tag>.

Codebase relies heavily on AB3's Person.

Require refactoring to function properly.

Let's
* edit prefix syntax to accommodate Description
* refactor instantiations of Person to the new Task object in JUnit tests.
* refactor logic for Person to the new Task object for parsing.
* refactor JUnit Testcases to handle Description
* refactor JUnit Testcases to handle logic relating to Task parsing
* edit JSON formats for default and testcases to handle new Task parameters.

GUI looks for PersonListCard/Panel.

Functions, testcases and FileNames still utilizes Person as the subject.

Rename these files and folders to Task as the subject
